description:
Terraria has been updated to the long awaited 1.2 patch, which introduces countless new blocks, items, weapons, biomes, bosses, and a whole lot of other great stuff into what was already an amazing game. Zisteau has invited me to join him as we both restart the game from scratch and discover all the changes that have been made.

Zisteau: http://www.youtube.com/user/Zisteau

Terraria Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/105600/
